node.text:
Switch out the ribbons on your Mother's Day gifts by preparing her a satisfying plate of ribbony Pappardelle with Spicy Salami for dinner! Famed for its handmade pastas, recreate luxurious resort food right in the comforts of your homes this Mother's Day with @SofitelSingaporeSentosa 𝐒𝐭𝐚𝐲 𝐇𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐑𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐩𝐞 𝐊𝐢𝐭𝐬.⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Exclusively curated to celebrate mothers worldwide for the entire month of May, take your pick on 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐏𝐞𝐫𝐟𝐞𝐜𝐭 𝐆𝐢𝐟𝐭! (link in bio) ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Find out more here: https://bit.ly/SofitelRecipeKits⁣⁣
⁣⁣
📷:@mykemotus ⁣
